	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_ECONOMIC_PLAYER_TRADE_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Projected Growth</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_ECONOMIC_PLAYER_TRADE_HELP">
			<Text>Our Economic Advisor has overseen the stockpiling of a significant amount of capital. She would now like to begin funding one of her pilot schemes. Which scheme should be given the green light?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_ECONOMIC_PLAYER_TRADE_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Spend {3_CityYieldGlobal} in each City in order to harvest an additional +1 [ICON_FOOD] Food from Farms, Plantations and Pastures for {4_Turns}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_ECONOMIC_PLAYER_TRADE_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Spend {3_CityYieldGlobal} in each City in order to expand excavations, yielding +2 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production from Mines and Quarries for {4_Turns}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_ECONOMIC_PLAYER_TRADE_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Spend {3_CityYieldGlobal} in each City in order to gain an additional +1 [ICON_GOLD] Gold from Coastal Tiles for {4_Turns}. Receive an additional +2 [ICON_GOLD] Gold if the Tile also hosts Fishing Boats.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_ECONOMIC_PLAYER_TRADE_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Fund artistic projects in every City, locally converting {3_CityYieldGlobal} for {4_Turns}.</Text>
		</Row>

		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_ECONOMIC_PLAYER_TRADE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>It is nearing harvest time, it strikes me that this agricultural exchange program would be very timely!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_ECONOMIC_PLAYER_TRADE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>This Empire is carried on the backs of its miners, they deserve any financial support we can muster!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_ECONOMIC_PLAYER_TRADE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Fishermen feed this people, it is high time they saw some formal support from the government!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_ECONOMIC_PLAYER_TRADE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>The countryside will get by with or without these schemes, it is the inner-cities that need our support in order to develop.</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
